      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "**Answer:**\n",
        "\n",
        "A real-world example of simple linear regression is predicting a person's weight based on their height. Height can be used as the independent variable, and weight as the dependent variable. The model can help estimate the weight of a person given their height."
